{"tid":1542073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰線] 穿雲箭已抵達北歐國家 The World is Watching","createTime":"2019-09-04T17:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T17:22:11.000Z","uid":198990,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ef62268c9e3984303cfc530854116984b39e74fe","tid":1542073,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:45:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入正題前再講多一句 <span style=\"color: red;\">膀胱壓測必須做</span> 原因容後再說<br />\n今日林太出賤招對淺黃既成效我諗大家都知 甫進家門我已經感受到嗰種威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國際既市井之民唔清楚香港現況之嚴峻 更加唔洗講<br />\n國際一直關注緊香港 遠至瑞典都有支持香港既活動<br />\n所以文宣手足 唔好放棄國際戰線 國際文宣一定要做 香港無贏<br />\n<br />\n早前同瑞典朋友傾香港情況 得知瑞典將於香港時間9月9日23:00集會支持香港示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSyaFpm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSyaFpm.png&h=a294503a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n除左文宣手足 希望在瑞典/有瑞典朋友既香港人可以將更多信息帶過去<br />\n都想俾當地人知道香港人收到佢地既支持 懇請佢地繼續支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/833734660354287/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F833734660354287%2F&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=bb5a4655\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/833734660354287/</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞典由運動初期已經有零星報導香港既抗爭 但內容有限 都唔預會多<br />\n始終鬼死咁遠 當睇下新聞知下就算<br />\n咁點解會發展到有一個集會活動呢? 就係轉捩點既出現: <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">812和你飛</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n812既經濟漣漪係偏及世界 瑞典開始報導更多香港既情況同新聞 因為影響到佢地經濟<br />\n朋友好直接同我講&quot;so obvious...even the west still only really care when they lose money&quot;<br />\n但係因為依個原因 報導越黎越多 亦令更多人真係睇到香港既情況 繼而關注香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">膀胱壓測必須做</span> 係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位手足 我地支持多將近3個月 好多絕望憤怒<br />\n但係唔好氣餒 遠至瑞典 The World is Watching 我們並不孤單<br />\n記著我地嘅約定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1340899903d5f880bbef0340c16c8dff3eff5880","tid":1542073,"uid":198990,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"Millions of Hongkongers has now for three months been demonstrating for their future. For Hongkongers, it&rsquo;s very risky to demand freedom and democratic rights, rights that we in Sweden still can take for granted. <span style=\"color: red;\">But even though the protesters are supported by millions it&rsquo;s like the fight between David and Goliath, since their counterpart is the very powerful and doesn&rsquo;t hesitate to use its power in a very violent way.</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The Hongkongers need our support, they need to see that the world sees what is going on and that they don&rsquo;t stand alone in their fight for freedom and democratic rights.</span><br />\n<br />\n最後嗰段我睇弱好感動 大家唔好放棄呀"},{"pid":"8ae22a13c49748552ba27d942d1e5e4ad4335d95","tid":1542073,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:49:03.000Z","msg":"【推上國際】Five Demands, ALL OR NONE<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542038</a><br />\n英文文宣啊 推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0739891b996e95eac5fbed98d03483c516ff08","tid":1542073,"uid":42981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:49:10.000Z","msg":"連結大愛國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1431e2cc6c774110924cc762b3aae7f451435f6","tid":1542073,"uid":42981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:49:39.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2473401f86e71a5d3f1d86a5fd364958e6ef5e3e","tid":1542073,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7943a3a97549d7e91fe1098e1e65a0bc2f2e1d","tid":1542073,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:52:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">907 膀胱壓測</div></span>"},{"pid":"a29af2494399129410e034748a4bba440afc1a70","tid":1542073,"uid":54946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:53:42.000Z","msg":"Scandinavian!"},{"pid":"f989cda7e04afcc6514dd5d006b9d7be7cc4ab4c","tid":1542073,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ec0580ba7fd0f9e7f96c1cb2a7d2aab383c7c9","tid":1542073,"uid":27993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:56:17.000Z","msg":"推!<br />\n要俾返瑞典知香港收到佢地支持<br />\n如果唔係佢地做完冇人知冇迴響就好難再做架啦"},{"pid":"3ad5f39f73798571e1e343a98f8728d3b1a74bc4","tid":1542073,"uid":27993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1340899903d5f880bbef0340c16c8dff3eff5880","tid":1542073,"uid":198990,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"Millions of Hongkongers has now for three months been demonstrating for their future. For Hongkongers, it&rsquo;s very risky to demand freedom and democratic rights, rights that we in Sweden still can take for granted. <span style=\"color: red;\">But even though the protesters are supported by millions it&rsquo;s like the fight between David and Goliath, since their counterpart is the very powerful and doesn&rsquo;t hesitate to use its power in a very violent way.</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The Hongkongers need our support, they need to see that the world sees what is going on and that they don&rsquo;t stand alone in their fight for freedom and democratic rights.</span><br />\n<br />\n最後嗰段我睇弱好感動 大家唔好放棄呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:57:01.000Z","msg":"even though the protesters are supported by millions it&rsquo;s like the fight between David and Goliath<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a5d7472be953473c540e53928e3a3f250a1137","tid":1542073,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:04:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59561b32cf1cd993fb45c79139cc3a821408e33b","tid":1542073,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ee793d483222873c15d567c6dd4be11f6ec6b9","tid":1542073,"uid":184919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:07:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c93aadbe92553d424a8c58d44dcec554df90d2aa","tid":1542073,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2355946d73de9681b31e825b01f75352e54307","tid":1542073,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1255bba3728a259e329d04a7a97e6cddd208c5","tid":1542073,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"Gratitude to Scandinavians!"},{"pid":"d377d21e3a7cd94ce374b822a617369dd53a0359","tid":1542073,"uid":166245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/l